description:
TDD Step 1: Define the abstraction layer for file operations.

## Test First
Write unit tests for IFileProvider interface contract:
- test_vfs_adapter.cpp with mock implementations
- Test local filesystem operations through interface
- Test URL scheme detection (s3://, gs://, az://, https://, file://)

## Implementation
Create src/include/vfs_adapter.hpp:
```cpp
class IFileProvider {
public:
    virtual ~IFileProvider() = default;
    virtual std::string ReadFile(const std::string& path) = 0;
    virtual bool FileExists(const std::string& path) = 0;
    virtual std::vector<std::string> ListFiles(const std::string& directory, const std::string& pattern) = 0;
    virtual bool IsRemotePath(const std::string& path) const = 0;
};

class LocalFileProvider : public IFileProvider { ... };
class DuckDBVFSProvider : public IFileProvider { ... };
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] IFileProvider interface defined with all required methods
- [ ] LocalFileProvider passes all existing file operation tests
- [ ] URL scheme detection correctly identifies remote paths
- [ ] Unit tests cover edge cases (empty paths, invalid schemes)
